title: Cancún Horror Story & International Travel Tips!
itunes:title: Cancún Horror Story & International Travel Tips!
description:
In this episode, Kimberly Cobb talks about her experience at the Charlotte Tilbury influencer event, shares her thoughts on internet trolls, recaps her Cancún horror story, gives away her best international travel tips, & more!

 

Follow for weekly episodes of the "My Lips Aren't Sealed" podcast, where I discuss dating, fashion, entertainment, travel, pop culture, and more from my life! Thanks for listening!
